'''Amcic''' ([[Assaɣ usnan]]: ''Felis catus'') d [[aɣersiw]] [[Timsiffatin|asuṭad]] [[Timseksumin|amseksum]] yeṭṭafaren [[tawacult (tasnudert)|tawacult]] n [[tiserɣuda|tserɣuda]], [[agrad|yessemgurd-it]] [[afgan|ufgan]] seg zik ɣef anect-a imusnawen ɣilen d akken yusa-d seg [[Abeṛṛay|ubeṛṛay]].

== Aglam ==
Amcic d aɣersiw meẓẓiyen maca ɣas akken [[Tasartut n tesnudert|yettusismel]] deg yiwet n twacult umi qqaren ''imcac imeqranen'' akk d [[Izem|yizem]], [[aɣilas]] d [[Aksil|weksil]], iɣersiwen-a yakk  qqaren-asen [[Tiserɣuda]]. Llan yemcac izagiren akked yemcac [[agrad|imegruden]].

[[Azuk]] n wemcic d win yettilin gar n 4 ar 7 kg (tikwal yettawaṭ ar 10 kg), yezmer ad [[asirem n tudert|yidir]] gar 12 ar 15 iseggasen. Maca llan waṭas n yemcac yettiwden ar 20 n iseggasen.

Amcic ila (yesɛa) [[iccer|accaren]] i yezmer ad ten-yesnejbad neɣ ad ten-id-yessuffeɣ melmi i yebɣa, [[Tinliwin|tinli]] n [[timesliwt|tmeskiwt]] ɣer wemcic d tin yernan (iɣelben) s waṭas n tikkal.

